      </small>
    </h2>
    <br>
    <div class="links">
      <a href="/" class="link" rel="noreferrer">Back To Home</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/Yoshiboi18303/Rocket" class="link" rel="noreferrer">Source Code</a>
      <a href="https://discord.gg/AC9FfKAxAa" class="link" rel="noreferrer">Support Server</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
  </body>
</html>